	<div class="container">
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Objective</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">I am seeking a position as a website developer that allows me to work remotely or is based within 50 miles of either Asheville, NC or Fredericksburg, VA.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Profile</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">I am a back-end web developer with 4.5 years of professional experience. I believe in being honest, reliable, and hardworking with a focus on customer satisfaction. I pride myself on being able to meet deadlines independently and without supervision, though I enjoy being part of a team and collaborating with other professionals. I am a citizen of the United Kingdom and a permanent resident of the United States.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Experience</span></p>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1"><b>CTO / Lead Web Developer,<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Ayutopia International; Fairview, NC — 2013-present</b></span></p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s1">As Chief Technology Officer, I manage the company’s technology initiatives, based on current best practices and industry standards. I evaluate and identify appropriate technology platforms for delivering the company’s services, managing internal projects, and serving client needs. I collaborate with other senior level executives, employees, and independent contractors. I monitor website analytics and give recommendations to improve performance. I ensure that technology standards and best practices are maintained across the organization and that technical problems are resolved in a timely and cost-effective manner.</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">As lead web developer, I build websites for both internal use and for clients. I am also in charge of managing the web hosting server.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">I interact with customers by phone and email to gather website requirements, answer questions, and fix any problems. Most of the websites I have built at Ayutopia are Wordpress based with customized PHP, JavaScript, CSS and MySQL. If required I would also provide clients with basic Wordpress lessons over Teamviewer or Skype.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">I created and published Ayutopia’s mobile app using HTML5 which is available in both the Apple app store and Google Play.</span></p>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1"><b>Web Developer, American Bankruptcy Institute; Alexandria ,VA — 2011-2013</b></span></p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s1">I worked on a number of websites for use by members of the American Bankruptcy Institute who include lawyers, judges, and the public looking for bankruptcy information. The majority of the websites I worked on were Drupal 6 and 7 based.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p5"><span class="s1">I was lead developer on one of ABI’s highest traffic websites (<a href="http://news.abi.org"><span class="s2">news.abi.org</span></a>) which received thousands of unique visitors a day.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p3"><span class="s1"><b>Web Developer Intern, TMG Custom Media; Washington D.C. — 2011</b></span></p>
<p class="p6"><span class="s1"><i>Note: TMG has merged with other companies and is now known as Manifest.</i></span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">I worked on a number of client websites, the majority of which were Drupal 5 and 6 based. I made front end changes to websites using CSS and provided graphics. I evaluated tools and plugins when given a problem that required solved.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Education</span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s1">Edinburgh Napier University; Scotland, UK</span></p>
<p class="p8"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>Bachelors of Science with Honors in Software Technology, 2009</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Skills</span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s1">Technology and Programming<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p9"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span>PHP, JavaScript/jQuery, AJAX, JSON/XML, HTML, CSS3, MySQL, HTML5 app development for iOS/ Android devices, Wordpress, Drupal, UNIX, web hosting management, website maintenance<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s1">Strategy and Planning<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
<p class="p10"><span class="s1">gather website requirements from clients; identify appropriate technology to support business goals; price out and plan time to completion of website; write proposal to submit to client;<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></span></p>
